      • EvuSearchLogicDlg

        public EvuSearchLogicDlg(java.awt.Frame owner,
                 java.lang.String title,
                 boolean modal,
                 EvuAnalysis dlg)
        Constructor for Evu Search Logic Dialog. References the VegLogicDialog superclass and passes the frame owner, dialog title, and modality. The last parameter is the Evu Analysis dialog.
        Parameters:
        owner - the frame which ownes the Evu Search Logic Dialog
        title - The title of the dialog
        modal - modality
        dlg - The Evu analysis dialog which has values for currently being analyzed.

      • EvuSearchLogicDlg

        public EvuSearchLogicDlg()
        Overloaded constructor for Evu Search Logic. References the default constructor and creates a new frame, title, modality = false, and null for Evu Analysis Dialog.

      • updateResults

        private void updateResults()
        Updates the results of search. If search units is null hides the results list and outputs no units found. Otherwise sets the results list with the list data of Evu result data Calculates acres by totaling acreage of evu's in search results.

      • menuOptionsMakeTreatments_actionPerformed

        void menuOptionsMakeTreatments_actionPerformed(java.awt.event.ActionEvent e)
        Gets the current area and treatment schedule for area. If there is no schedule, creates one. Otherwise creates a new treatment dialog to allow user to select a treatment. First a time step is picked by user, then the user picks the treatment, and adds the Evu units to the treatments units.
        Parameters:
        e - 'Make Treatments'
